"are the streets called? Which administrative regions do certain areas belong"
" to? What are the relative surface areas of the farms? All of this "
"information is still hidden. The next lesson will explain how to represent "
"this data on your map."
msgstr ""
"Att ГӨndra symboler fГ¶r hela lager ГӨr anvГӨndbart, men informationen i varje "
"lager ГӨr ГӨnnu inte tillgГӨnglig fГ¶r nГҘgon som lГӨser dessa kartor. Vad kallas "
"gatorna? Vilka administrativa regioner tillhГ¶r vissa omrГҘden? Vilka ГӨr "
"gГҘrdarnas relativa ytor? All denna information ГӨr fortfarande dold. I nГӨsta "
"lektion fГ¶rklaras hur du kan representera dessa data pГҘ din karta."

